column1: Being single for a while now has been a learning experience and a process, but I am now very confident in knowing who I am, what I like, what kind of person I want in my life and that I simply can't settle. Last step in this journey is to figure out where to find the woman that fits into this wonderful life of mine. I love my faith, animals, clothing, textile design, sports, traveling, the outdoors, historical architecture and culture, learning new things, laughing and having a good time. Accepting of people for who they are not what they look like or what they have wrong medically. I am a hard worker and I like to know that I am being productive and that my life has order. I don't exactly wish people would notice anything; I just feel like sometimes, people notice or judge my physical appearance & don't think far enough past that. I'm sensitive & thoughtful & very different than what they often expect. It's kind of fun to turn it all around & show them who I am. My hobbies and interests are golfing, riding my motorcycle, and hiking, seeing new sights and re-visiting some favorite ones. I play poker, have a dynamite poker face, love to travel and take Philosophies I live by are Life is about the journey, not the destination. I am a better man today than I was yesterday and I strive to be a better man tomorrow than I am today.,"I'm looking for a woman who will be my best friend. Someone I can talk with, play with, laugh with. Who is fun and makes me laugh, who is smart and makes me think, who will walk with me on my journey with God wherever it leads. Mostly of all i love truth and hate lies because when there is lie then no trust and when there is no trust then no love. Someone who is open to me making them think, too. I'm looking for someone who is passionate and not afraid of intimacy, both emotional and physical . We'll go dancing, stay at home and cook dinner or watch a movie, go to the theater, share a life and maybe some day have kids maybe yours, maybe ours, or maybe adopt someone else or foster. With integrity, compassion and we will love each other for every. column1:
Simplicity and honesty are the two adjectives that describe a good human being the best. I am one of those people and feel blessed to have inherited these qualities. People around me appreciate me for the same and I am in the good books of many people I like. 
I am very practical as a person. This has helped me in being up to date with the world. I do not believe everything anyone says. I need reasons to believe people. Being reasonable has helped me in increasing my knowledge. 
I am a business man and I deal with tours and travels. I like my work and I find it very interesting. I hope I get success in this field. If I do, I will be grateful to the people who have helped me. 
My mother is a homemaker and my brother is a business man. He is married and his wife is homemaker. I lost my father and now I miss him a lot. I will always miss him and no one can take his place. I take care of my family and can do anything they ask me to do. 
I am quite modern as a person and that I think is something good in me. Being modern is very important in todaya??s scenario, as one cannot adjust if one is traditional. 
When I get some time off, I like to listen to music and watch movies. I also like travelling to different places.,"I will prefer marrying a girl from Mumbai because if she is from there she will already be aware of the area plus she will be familiar with the culture and customs people follow there. This way she will take less time in adjusting.
Also, if she is from Mumbai she can visit her parents whenever she misses them without travelling much.

She should be educated as I value education more than anything else. If she is educated, she will be a decent person automatically. She needs to be very loyal. This will not only make her win my trust but will also help me in sharing things with her as this is something that is very important for a sound and a healthy relationship. If we both are loyal to each other, we can become a good couple.

When a person gets married, the whole family has to love each other and respect each other. I will expect the same from my partner. She should be very respectful towards my parents and elders in my family. If she respects them, I am sure I will give her parents the same respect.

I am very honest as a person and I will expect the same honesty in my partner. A relationship is a weak thread. It gets weaker if people are not honest with each other. I am sure that our relationship will get stronger if we will be loyal and honest to each other.
,,,29 Dec 1965,,India,,,,,Jain-Others,,,,,,Self,12th,47 yrs, 5ft 8in,
